# 13.11 Three of a Kind by Cards Pattern (13 variants)
# ThreeOfAKindByCardsBestHand: minQualifiedCardinality 3 for each rank.
# Note: also detects Full House (has trips) and Four of a Kind (4 >= 3).

poker:ThreeOfAKindByCardsBestHand a owl:Class ;
    owl:equivalentClass [
        a owl:Class ;
        owl:intersectionOf (
            poker:BestHand
